  "_instructions": [
    "HOW TO ADD NEW ANIMATIONS:",
    "1. Create folder in .dances/ with your animation files",
    "2. Add camera JSON files to the folder",
    "3. Create configuration INI file (AnimationName.ini) in the folder",
    "4. Add entry to 'animations' array above",
    "5. List ALL camera files in 'cameraFiles' array",
    "6. Specify configuration file in 'configFile' property",
    "",
    "CONFIGURATION FILES:",
    "- Each animation has its own INI file in its folder",
    "- Name format: AnimationName.ini (must match configFile property)",
    "- Contains animation-specific settings (delay, camera offsets, etc.)",
    "- Global settings (theme, progress bar, pause text) are in userConfig.ini",
    "",
    "CAMERA FILES ARRAY:",
    "- List ALL camera JSON files for this animation",
    "- Order doesn't matter (will be sorted alphabetically)",
    "- First file in list = default camera",
    "- Can have 1 to 10 camera files per animation",
    "",
    "FIELD DESCRIPTIONS:",
    "- id: Unique number (must be different from all others)",
    "- name: Internal name (must match folder name)",
    "- displayName: Name shown in menu",
    "- folder: Folder name in .dances/",
    "- animPackage: IFP package name",
    "- animName: Animation name in IFP",
    "- audioFile: MP3 filename",
    "- cameraFiles: Array of camera JSON filenames",
    "- configFile: Configuration INI filename"
  ]
}
